The paper discusses deep learning architectures, specifically Neural ODEs, and their connection to dynamical systems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper introduces novel architectures, which could also place it in the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also discuss applications of Neural ODEs in computer vision, which could place it in the Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-category.
